{"tid":235763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣囝上水又唔敢開post 淨係縮係佢自己個單機中介post","createTime":"2017-05-09T08:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T03:38:53.000Z","uid":19493,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"271b984ed355e025df9a3cd60b5d54aae8dbe8f4","tid":235763,"uid":19493,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:52:23.000Z","msg":"諗到佢伸個龜頭出嚟裝下裝下個樣 就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7b0fb359a504aa5ce86f96e8f19e67efbd3db4","tid":235763,"uid":19493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:53:36.000Z","msg":"蔣介石(翻生) 懶人包<br />\n禮賢會時期:<br />\n1. 中三非禮同學 &lt;&mdash;&mdash; 被舊同學踢爆 被逼轉校<br />\n2. 起同班嘅女同學底 WhatsApp同人講我知你住邊到。<br />\n做 project 果陣 好似咩都唔做 freerider然後又同班男同學嗌交 <br />\n玩同學電話 叫咗五百幾蚊外賣上人屋企 <br />\n玩埋同學嘅家姐 然後係班群 嗌交 出嚟隻揪，然後上堂果陣成隻死狗咁 一落堂就鼠走咗。佢屋企人係律師嚟，科主任因爲依單嘢 出咗警告信，佢後尾疑似轉咗去 觀塘ive.<br />\n3. 老屈舊校新校長係殺人犯<br />\n<br />\n高登時期:<br />\n1.<a href=\"http://forum1.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=ET&amp;message=6493169&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=29&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum1.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DET%26message%3D6493169%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D29%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=def13de2\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum1.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=ET&amp;message=6493169&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=29&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n上高登諗住唱衰自己學校，點知俾人踢爆係ON9仔，俾人起哂facebook 學校老師都知<br />\n<br />\n連登時期:<br />\n1.屌柒中介有功一朝得志，自命連登救星，四處辣火頭<br />\n2.周圍屈人，每日係facebook搵料公審人，逢質疑件事真確性就自動變成五毛/中介/波台狗<br />\n3.貼兩張律師卡片恐嚇侮辱佢既巴打<br />\n4. 要求被指控者提出證據證明自己清白<br />\n5. 屌波台5P低質，自己facebook金句都用5p字<br />\n6. 涉嫌報刑事案件期間於LIHKG討論區張貼口供紙<br />\n7. 懷疑恐嚇LIHKG會員 令其傾家蕩產<br />\n8.吹水作故仔話去咗報警，點知俾一眾巴打踢爆<br />\n9. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">懷疑刑事恐嚇連登會員鐵樹蘭開花</span></span><br />\n10.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 懷疑冒認舊校慕光英文書院某老師，企圖呃9馬車去做表演嘉賓<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ocatequista.com.br/images/catecismo_muppets.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Focatequista.com.br%2Fimages%2Fcatecismo_muppets.gif&h=49fb90c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55dba326ca1df0aac5ccfe92b229e6fcf29ec857","tid":235763,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://bestanimations.com/Animals/Mammals/Dolphins/dolphin/dolphin-jumping-animated-gif-5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbestanimations.com%2FAnimals%2FMammals%2FDolphins%2Fdolphin%2Fdolphin-jumping-animated-gif-5.gif&h=ae89264e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醬囝上水負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834007719af1c8b30afdc3c5df36b2adcadf5e05","tid":235763,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"佢繼續狙擊中介,你繼續係度狙擊佢咪好囉"},{"pid":"90d09c3ced2172b4125e0e32a45e1800433eebb5","tid":235763,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"有關叫高登收皮一事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/174300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/174300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n澄清&quot;[極醜惡】【高登淪亡】疑似高登仔ig性騒擾少女&quot;一事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/171473/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/171473/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n就誤解41J一事深表歉意<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/171932/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/171932/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n由蔣巴變蔣狗 談連登質素 (蔣介石於第3頁被起底)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/200697/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.